a:9:{s:7:"attribs";a:2:{s:5:"xmlns";s:36:"http://pear.php.net/dtd/rest.package";s:18:"xsi:schemaLocation";s:80:"http://pear.php.net/dtd/rest.package    http://pear.php.net/dtd/rest.package.xsd";}s:1:"n";s:19:"Auguria_Sponsorship";s:1:"c";s:37:"connect.magentocommerce.com/community";s:2:"ca";a:2:{s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:10:"xlink:href";s:34:"/Chiara_PEAR_Server_REST/c/Default";}s:8:"_content";s:7:"Default";}s:1:"l";s:27:"Open Software License (OSL)";s:2:"lu";s:42:"http://opensource.org/licenses/osl-3.0.php";s:1:"s";s:69:"This module allows customers to earn fidelity and sponsorship points.";s:1:"d";s:6186:"<p><strong>The module consists of :</strong><br /><br />- A form to send invitations: when an invitation is sent, the guest mail is registered, and the customer id too. Invitations can be sent with <a href="http://openinviter.com/">OpenInviter</a>.<br /><br />- A system of affiliation: You can add sponsor_id param to each page, that will create a cookie and a session to identify a person invited.&nbsp; We can equally put such links on third party sites. And we rewrite <a href="../../../magento-connect/_Fluxe/extension/2333/magento-social-bookmarking">Magentix_SocialBookmarking</a> module to allow sponsorship with.<br /><br />- Account creation: When creating an account, it checks whether an invitation was sent to the email used for registration. If this is not the case, we check if a session cookie or affiliation exists. If there is a link, the user who registers become the godson of the customer who invits him.<br /><br />- A monitoring points for the client: the client have an interface for monitoring points in his account. He can see his godson. He can ask for trade his points.<br /><br />- Increment of points: Fidelity points and sponsorship points are inserted in the command, at the checkout cart. Upon payment of the command, points are awarded to customers.<br /><br />- Definition of rules: the management of points can be made through the catalog rules prices or cart rules prices.<br /><br />- Module configuration: The administration interface allows you to enable or disable fidelity points or sponsorship points. Enabling or no exchange of cash, gift or coupon. You can also define the max cash without siret number, the period of calcul of the max cash, if an order is required to sponsor, the period of validity for an invitation, the period of validity of a sponsorship whithout an order, number of levels for sponsorship calculation points, the percentage on indirect sponsorship sales, the maximum number of invitations that you can send per hour, the header message, the body message and the footer message.<br /><br />- An administration interface: allows to see the list of invitations sent, monitor requests for trade of points.<br /><br /><strong>Once installed, you must:</strong><br /><br />- Create one or several catalog or cart rules for increment fidelity and sponsorship points<br /><br />- Edit CMS Page on sponsorship information<br /><br />- If you enable automatic sponsorship recall, activate magento cron</p>
<p>- Create an <a href="http://openinviter.com/">OpenInviter</a> account, and active this feature inta confi of sponsorship module.</p>
<p><br /><br /><br />################################<br /><br /><strong>Le module comporte :</strong><br /><br />- Un formulaire pour envoyer des invitations. Il est possible d'utiliser <a href="http://openinviter.com/">OpenInviter</a> pour envoyer les invitations.<br /><br />- Un syst&egrave;me d'affiliation par email, &agrave; partir d'un site tiers ou avec <a href="../../../magento-connect/_Fluxe/extension/2333/magento-social-bookmarking">Magentix_SocialBookmarking</a>.<br /><br />- Un compl&eacute;ment pour la cr&eacute;ation de compte afin de rattacher le nouveau client &agrave; son parrain ou &agrave; son affiliateur.<br /><br />- Une interface de contr&ocirc;le : les parrains et affiliateurs ont une interface pour la surveillance des points sur leur compte. Ils peuvent voir leurs filleuls et demander l'&eacute;change des points obtenus (cash, bon cadeau).<br /><br />- D&eacute;finition des r&egrave;gles : l'attribution des points se fait avec les r&egrave;gles de prix catalogue et les r&egrave;gles de prix panier.<br /><br />- Configuration du module : L'interface d'administration permet d'activer ou de d&eacute;sactiver les points de fid&eacute;lit&eacute; et ou de parrainage. D'activer ou pas l'&eacute;change en cash ou en coupon. Vous pouvez aussi d&eacute;finir un maximum pour l'&eacute;change en cash, la p&eacute;riode de calcul pour le maximum d'&eacute;change en cash, si une commande est n&eacute;cessaire pour parrainer, la p&eacute;riode de validit&eacute; d'une invitation sans commande, le nombre de niveaux pour le calcul des points de parrainage, le pourcentage sur les parrainages indirects, le nombre maximum d'invitations par heure, l'ent&ecirc;te des messages, le corps des messages, et le pied de page des messages.<br /><br />- Une interface d'administration : permet de voir la liste des invitations envoy&eacute;es, de g&eacute;rer les demandes d'&eacute;change de points.<br /><br /><strong>Une fois install&eacute;, vous devez :</strong><br /><br />- Cr&eacute;er vos r&egrave;gles de prix catalogue ou panier pour attribuer les points de fid&eacute;lit&eacute; et de parrainage<br /><br />- Modifier la page CMS sponsorship information<br /><br />- Si vous activez le rappel automatique des invitations, activer les cron Magento</p>
<p>- Cr&eacute;ez un compte <a href="http://openinviter.com/">OpenInviter</a>, et  activez cette fonctionnalit&eacute; dans l'administration du module sponsorship.<br /><br />Ce module a &eacute;t&eacute; d&eacute;velopp&eacute; &agrave; l'origine pour le site <a href="http://www.inkonso.com">www.inkonso.com</a> par la soci&eacute;t&eacute; <strong><a href="http://www.auguria.net">Auguria</a></strong><br /><br /><br />=============== <strong>Releases</strong> ===============</p>
<p>You can install this extension in magento <strong>1.3 but only with Version 0.1.4 of this extension </strong>(go in releases)<br /><br />1.0.0 first release<br /><br />1.0.1 separate magento 1.3 and 1.4 release, fix bug with prefixed tables, change, fix bug getting rules in validator, separate fidelity and sponsorship customer views</p>
<p>1.0.2 remove eregi deprecated method</p>
<p>1.0.3 Add affiliate to each pages, add <a href="http://openinviter.com/">OpenInviter</a> to sponsorship, save sponsorship form data into customer session, resolve bug to display sponsorship in admin (due to 1.4.1 release)</p>
<p>1.0.4 Update Mage_Adminhtml_Block_Widget_Grid_Container extends to resolve display bugs, add select of open inviter providers images in backoffice, add sponsor id to Magentix_SocialBookmarking</p>";s:1:"r";a:1:{s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:10:"xlink:href";s:46:"/Chiara_PEAR_Server_REST/r/Auguria_Sponsorship";}}}